{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd1520045-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s1911"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1911"},"text":"§ 1911.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional annual authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1520046-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s1911/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In addition to amounts that may be made available to the Secretary under the Fund for a fiscal year, there is authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary for each fiscal year, beginning with fiscal year 2020, $16,000,000, to carry out the grant program for the National Flagship Language Initiative under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1902/a/1/D"},"text":"section 1902(a)(1)(D) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1520047-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s1911/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Funding from Intelligence Community Management Account for fiscal years beginning with fiscal year 2005","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In addition to amounts that may be made available to the Secretary under the Fund for a fiscal year, the Director of National Intelligence shall transfer to the Secretary from amounts appropriated for the Intelligence Community Management Account for each of fiscal years 2005 through 2021 $6,000,000 to carry out the grant program for the National Flagship Language Initiative under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1902/a/1/D"},"text":"section 1902(a)(1)(D) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1520048-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s1911/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Availability of appropriated funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amounts made available under this section shall remain available until expended.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd1520049-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/183/tVIII/s811"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–183, title VIII, § 811","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/306/tIII/s333/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–306, title III, § 333(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-27"},"text":"Nov. 27, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/2397"},"text":"116 Stat. 2397","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/487/tVI/s602/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–487, title VI, § 602(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/3953"},"text":"118 Stat. 3953","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92/dA/tXVI/s1623"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92, div. A, title XVI, § 1623","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 2019","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/133/1735"},"text":"133 Stat. 1735","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/260/dW/tVI/s619/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–260, div. W, title VI, § 619(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/2401"},"text":"134 Stat. 2401","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd152004a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd152004b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idd152004c-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2020—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/260/s619/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–260, § 619(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “$16,000,000” for “$10,000,000”, could not be executed because “$10,000,000” did not appear in text after the amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":". See 2019 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/260/s619/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–260, § 619(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “for each of fiscal years 2005 through 2021” for “for each fiscal year, beginning with fiscal year 2005,”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":", which directed amendment of section 811(a) of the Fair Chance Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1911/a"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 1911(a)","children":[],"tail":") by substituting “fiscal year 2020” for “fiscal year 2003” and “$16,000,000” for “$10,000,000”, was executed to subsec. (a) of this section, which is section 811 of the David L. Boren National Security Education Act of 1991, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—Subsecs. (b), (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/487"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–487","children":[],"tail":" added subsecs. (b) and (c) and struck out heading and text of former subsec. (b). Text read as follows: “Amounts appropriated pursuant to the authorization of appropriations under subsection (a) shall remain available until expended.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idd154493d-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"idd154493e-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective on the date the Secretary of Defense submits the report required under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/306/s334"},"text":"section 334 of Pub. L. 107–306","children":[],"tail":" and notifies the appropriate committees of Congress that the programs carried out under this chapter are being managed in a fiscally and programmatically sound manner, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/306/s333/c"},"text":"section 333(c) of Pub. L. 107–306","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 2002 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1902"},"text":"section 1902 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
